title: Little Bird Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A hip cafe in Northbridge offering vegan options including its signature giant buckwheat pancake, plus has smoothies, raw lasagna, and vegetarian items. Staff is accommodating for dietary requirements. Uses organic, better quality ingredients. Prices are slightly higher.
